title: Monocacy National Battlefield: Guest Speakers
body: Explore This Park    Learn About the Park     Education     Parks as Classrooms     Guest Speakers                Guest Speakers          Invite a Ranger to Your Class! If you are unable to come to the park, a park ranger or volunteer will be happy to come to your class to talk about the park or some aspect of its history. Call 301-662-3515 to schedule a guest speaker.
